    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Dylan's Song\r\n\r\nAn **algorithm** is a series of steps to accomplish a task. For example, your friend Dylan has been working on this great intro riff for a new song:\r\n\r\n1) First we used the **Arena** beat with the **Fuzz Drop** bass and the **Ghost Choir** lead\r\n2) Then we kicked it up a notch by repeating those three and adding a **Crash** effect\r\n3) Then we changed the lead to the **Buzz Riff** guitar instead\r\n\r\nFollow Dylan's **algorithm** to recreate this song. You can listen to the song below. Your song should match his exactly!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/b91fe6d80fa5bd8bdbea7603d1c0a803-image-1742935354574.png)",
